sg":"每個人都有自己諗法，點解一定要統一晒所有黃絲支持一邊或者兩面都唔支持?"},{"pid":"f24a513a316edbc9c31fc8003a0fad5e0e07a283","tid":2044014,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae916635eeaa44ccaa3f9c48041b647578a1cbb0","tid":2044014,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T20:57:05.000Z","msg":"同左膠鬥左膠<br />\n我嘅願望係世界和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T21:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">[港獨強心針]</div><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">香港最強力盟友USA : <br />\n國際反共形勢大好<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2041520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2041520</a></span></div>"},{"pid":"2edfafa6270fc9ae817a492d9471ab03ae1261e2","tid":2044014,"uid":247719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T21:48:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01113ccefa905206f784ec52047edd4259054b90","tid":2044014,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8c35830e226f05a7ee40e95b100353f29a72011","tid":2044014,"uid":45761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T21:19:29.000Z","msg":"&quot;希望美國衝突盡快結束，社會回復平靜&quot;<br />\n呢句都唔好講啦,你唔知果邊D人而家咩心態<br />\n你諗返上年示威最高漲果期見到人講D咁既野會唔會火都黎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝下人平安咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T21:54:57.000Z","msg":"咁都係因為你不自覺代入緊抗爭者既角色<br />\n計番比例 美國人有參與示威既人數 絕對仲少過香港抗爭者<br />\n佢地未必有發聲 但一樣睇緊twitter<br />\n你要想象 你係twitter講既每一句說話 係俾成個美國既人睇"},{"pid":"6fa0c97b7c48c95f8d395c5771cd5c2beb7f6cce","tid":2044014,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T21:55:51.000Z","msg":"成件事同香港只有一個共通點 就係有警暴<br />\n<br />\n唔同嘅係人哋<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民選政府要照顧民意 <br />\n會按法律去制裁黑暴</strong></span><br />\n由當日殺死黑人 到今日開槍鎮壓都係<br />\n人哋警察要為自己行為負責任<br />\n<br />\n唔需要將香港示威同件事扯上其他關係<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BWmydpd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBWmydpd.png&h=b39176bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZL5bKvU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZL5bKvU.png&h=863f50d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kXTQfCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkXTQfCA.jpg&h=9d4e0e11&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}